<h2>No Dance for the Cowboy</h2>
<h3>Chapter 3</h3>
<img src="/images/dancingcowboy/pict_3.jpg" alt="the case of the dancing cowboy" />
<p>Hey, let's get something straight right now. Just because a dog snaps at ashes, that doesn't mean ... One of the very most important functions 
    of a Head of Ranch Security is research and development. Your R&D work -- 
