<img src="/images/dancingcowboy/pict_4.jpg" alt="the case of the dancing cowboy" />
<p>I raced to the pickup. 
    Slim hadn't gotten there yet to open the door but that was no big deal to 
    me. Hey, if they don't open the door, I can always jump through the ... 
